item.title: Machinelearning resources from Devopsdays Oslo 2017
item.description: At Devopsdays Oslo 2017, there was a discussion about machine learning at one of the one of the openspace sessions. I made some notes from the session, and put it into a gist that I shared on twitter. This is essentially that gist, so not much editing here.
